OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772554283
OL,3,C'Misfire' could have caused rifle to
OL,4,Cfire, killing soldier
OL,6,FA "misfire" by a sniper rifle could
OL,7,Fhave caused the death of a soldier who
OL,8,Fdied of a fatal gunshot to the head
OL,9,Fwhile waiting to go on a firing range
OL,10,Fin the Scottish Highlands, an inquest
OL,11,Fhas heard.
OL,13,FLance Corporal Joe Spencer, 24, from
OL,14,FHampshire, was killed on November 1
OL,15,F2016 when an L115A3 sniper rifle fired
OL,16,Fa round while he was sheltering from
OL,17,Fthe rain at the Tain Air Weapons Range.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
